Why Greatest Hits, Vol. 1 best matches these preferences: 
- Tape‑warm sheen and preserved transients: the CD explicitly offers a tape‑warm sheen with preserved transients and generous headroom — this matches my desire for analog warmth and preserved micro‑dynamics instead of loudness‑crushed mastering. 
